<h2 class=3D"wp-block-heading" id=3D"h-calculate-coordinates-of-targets-in-=
a-grid">Calculate Coordinates of Targets in a Grid</h2>



<p>A useful interactive application that calculates the coordinates of the =
centers of cells in an N x N grid. Perfect for working out where to place t=
argets / images in visual world, visual search, and saccade paradigms. Inpu=
t your screen resolution and desired number of rows / columns. There is als=
o an option to add a border. Output is a list of coordinate pairs (left to =
right, top to bottom) that can be copied and pasted for use in Experiment B=
uilder or other stimulus presentation software.</p>



